{
  "stem": "1603.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But one man, one captain, was so angry at Hannah, because Hannah just-- I mean, spitted at these Nazis and yelled and used harsh language and everything and was very brave.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So just about a week before the Russians came in and took over, this captain ran into the prison and had no right or no papers from any judge to execute her.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But she had her carried to the execution place and had her executed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's how she died.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You saw that or you read that?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I read that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- but I know from-- from the fact that she has a monument in Israel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think my father sent some-- some livestock to Israel to the kibbutz where she wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I don't think she ever arrived there, because I don't think she went any farther than London.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think she came back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother came down from this place, and then what happened, I wanted to be with my mother and sister.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we went-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] let me see how it happened.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, so my mother and my sister lived in this apartment on Buda part in Budapest, and then for some reason, I don't know why, but in that Catholic school we couldn't stay any longer where we stayed.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Alexander, who saved my sister's and mother's life, came for my rescue and took him-- took me into his apartment.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was hiding me out in his apartment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But what happened, Alexander's mother would come to Alexander's apartment, not as his mother but as a lady-- as a cleaning lady.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
